Presentation Notes:
Rewriting the Massey GameEngine to separate out responsibilities of managing graphics, physics
Iterate beginning with simple case
Complex Menu
Two player
Bad apples reduce health
Doom Face style avatar
Future Improvements:
- include obstacles like walls or rocks
- include power ups
- refactor to use game states
- display high scores
## Snek
Snek: loosely based on EC system, logical and graphical representation separated out, snek handles key events itself and will grow as necessary, largely manages itself aside from responding to collisions and needing to be told when to eat an apple. insert image here. A higher level (whatever this is) manages the interactions between actors.
